page.title: 37Garages and Transport 2
page.content:
There are still many garages or businesses related to transport in Rumblingwell. Abbey Cars, Osbourne Motors, Orwell Motors, Glen Motors, Dunfermline Motor Company and Simpson Motors all sell used cars.

Simpson Motors opened in 1986 and sell about 200 cars p.a. D&G Autocare opened in 2004 and they repair about 70 cars a week. Trix repairs dents and scratches. There was a ‘BP’ petrol station it is now a carwash. Centaur Motors (Peuguot) and Curtis Motors (Vauxhall) were both knocked down.
